thread.title: PSM Construction Services Inc.
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by PSM Construction Services Inc.

author: PSM Construction Services Inc.
title: PSM Construction Services Inc.
text:
I have dealt with this company twice to date within the past 6 months and the level of service has been excellent.
The quality of the eyewear, lenses are also a very good quality and the pricing is competitive.
I will certainly use and have already recommended them to my wife and family.
Is nice to know there are still companies out there that truly believe in customer service!
Keep up ye good work!
Bwm
